### **TC_AMZ_004: Verify Product Details Display**

**Priority:** HIGH | **Type:** Smoke Test | **Automation:** YES

**Test Objective:**  
Validate that product details page displays all required information

**Pre-conditions:**
- Execute TC_AMZ_001 (be on search results page)
- At least one product result is visible

**Test Data:**
```
Use: First product from search results
```

**Detailed Test Steps:**

| Step | Action | Element Details | Expected Result | Automation Notes |
|------|--------|----------------|----------------|------------------|
| 1 | Locate first product in results | CSS: `[data-component-type="s-search-result"]` (first) | Product card visible | `driver.findElements(...).get(0)` |
| 2 | Store product title for validation | CSS: `.a-size-medium.a-color-base.a-text-normal` (within first result) | Title text captured | `String expectedTitle = element.getText()` |
| 3 | Click on first product | CSS: `.s-image` or the title link | - | `element.click()` |
| 4 | Wait for product page load | ID: `productTitle` visible | Product page loads | `wait.until(visibilityOfElementLocated(By.id("productTitle")))` |
| 5 | Verify product title matches | ID: `productTitle` | Title contains keywords from search | Compare with stored title |
| 6 | Verify product image displayed | ID: `landingImage` or CSS: `#imgTagWrapperId img` | Image is visible | `element.isDisplayed()` |
| 7 | Verify product price displayed | CSS: `.a-price-whole` or ID: `priceblock_ourprice` | Price is visible | Check element exists |
| 8 | Verify product rating | CSS: `.a-icon-star` or `[data-hook="rating-out-of-text"]` | Rating (e.g., "4.5 out of 5") shown | Extract rating value |
| 9 | Verify reviews count | ID: `acrCustomerReviewText` | Text like "1,234 ratings" shown | Extract count |
| 10 | Verify "Add to Cart" button | ID: `add-to-cart-button` | Button is visible and enabled | `element.isEnabled()` |
| 11 | Verify "Buy Now" button | ID: `buy-now-button` | Button visible | Optional check |
| 12 | Verify product description | ID: `feature-bullets` or `productDescription` | Description text present | Check text length > 50 chars |

**Expected Final Result:**
- Product page displays completely
- All key elements present: title, image, price, rating, Add to Cart button
- Page is interactive (not loading)

**Automation Notes:**
```java
// Validate all key elements
Assert.assertTrue(driver.findElement(By.id("productTitle")).isDisplayed(), "Title missing");
Assert.assertTrue(driver.findElement(By.id("landingImage")).isDisplayed(), "Image missing");
Assert.assertTrue(driver.findElement(By.id("add-to-cart-button")).isEnabled(), "Add to Cart not enabled");

// Extract and validate rating
String ratingText = driver.findElement(By.cssSelector(".a-icon-star")).getText();
Assert.assertTrue(ratingText.contains("out of 5"), "Rating format incorrect");
```

