## üìä **TEST DATA SETS FOR DATA-DRIVEN TESTING**

### **Search Keywords Test Data (search_data.xlsx)**

| Test ID | Keyword | Expected Min Results | Category | Test Type |
|---------|---------|---------------------|----------|-----------|
| TD_001 | laptop | 50 | Electronics | Valid |
| TD_002 | wireless mouse | 30 | Electronics | Valid |
| TD_003 | books | 100 | Books | Valid |
